com.example.sickar.main

Class DataViewModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
      • androidx.lifecycle.AndroidViewModel
        • com.example.sickar.main.DataViewModel

  • public class DataViewModel
extends androidx.lifecycle.AndroidViewModel
    ViewModel for main activity. This ViewModel abstracts away the cache from mainActivity and contains LiveData objects which are updated by network responses in the background. Once a LiveData object is updated its corresponding observers will be notified in the MainActivity to update the appropriate views.
